<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الإِنسان،<span class="c5"> والأكمه:</span> الذي يولد أعمى،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> وَتُبْرِئُ الْأَكْمَهَ وَالْأَبْرَصَ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وقد يسمى العمى العارضُ كمهاً، وهو قول سويد بن أبي كاهل <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>كمهت عيناه حتى ابيضتا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ي]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[كمي]</span>: يقال: كمِي عن الأخبار: إِذا جهلها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[همزة]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[كمِئ]</span>: كمِئت رجله،<span class="c5"> بالهمزة:</span> إِذا تشققت.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>... فعُل، يفعُل، بالضم<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[ت]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[كَمُت]</span> الفرس كُمْتَة وكَمَاتة.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[ش]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[كَمُش]</span> كماشة فهو كميش: أي سريع.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[كَمُل]</span>: الكمال: التمام.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>... الزيادة<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>الإِفعال<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[الإِكماح]</span>: أكمح الفرسَ: إِذا جذب عنانه لينتصب رأسه.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[د]</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c4">[الإِكماد]</span>: أكمده الحزنُ.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وأكمد القصارُ الثوبَ.<span class="c5"> ويقال:</span> كمده بغير همزة.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
